article.description: — Dravon Mangum had 16 points as Radford romped past Charleston Southern 68-48 on Sunday.
article.headline: Mangum carries Radford past Charleston Southern 68-48
article.linkText: Mangum carries Radford past Charleston Southern 68-48
article.story: CHARLESTON, S.C. -- — Dravon Mangum had 16 points as Radford romped past Charleston Southern 68-48 on Sunday. Fah’Mir Ali had 12 points and six rebounds for Radford (8-6, 7-1 Big South Conference), which won its fourth straight game. Chyree Walker added nine rebounds. Phlandrous Fleming Jr. had 18 points for the Buccaneers (1-9, 0-6), whose losing streak reached six games. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
